{"id": "27933", "post": "<div class=\"post-27933 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-com tag-domain tag-domain-registration tag-namesilo tag-verisign\" id=\"post-27933\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/verisign-increasing-com-fees-september-1-namesilo-increasing-them-even-more/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Verisign Increasing .COM Fees September 1. NameSilo Increasing Them Even More</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/com/\" rel=\"tag\">.com</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/domain/\" rel=\"tag\">domain</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/domain-registration/\" rel=\"tag\">domain registration</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/namesilo/\" rel=\"tag\">namesilo</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/verisign/\" rel=\"tag\">verisign</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> August 6, 2021 @ 12:00 pm, by raindog308</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/verisign.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-27934 litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/verisign.png\" alt=\"verisign logo\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" align=\"right\" hspace=\"20\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/verisign.png 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/verisign-150x150.png 150w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/verisign.png 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/verisign-150x150.png 150w\" data-was-processed=\"true\"><br>\nSorry to harsh your summer buzz, but that <a href=\"https://www.verisign.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"verisign\">Verisign</a> announcement from back in February that you briefly grumbled about and then forgot because it was in the future is now relevant. As of September 1, your .com costs are going up.</p><p>Well, unless you have an incredibly charitable registrar. Which you don\u2019t. You don\u2019t buy directly from Verisign so here for example is how <a href=\"https://www.namesilo.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"namesilo\">NameSilo</a>, a popular community registrar, is reacting:</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/namesilo_price_increase_450.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-27938 size-full litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/namesilo_price_increase_450.png\" alt=\"namesilo prices 450\" width=\"450\" height=\"256\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/namesilo_price_increase_450.png 450w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/namesilo_price_increase_450-300x171.png 300w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/namesilo_price_increase_450.png 450w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/namesilo_price_increase_450-300x171.png 300w\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></p><p>Ouch.&nbsp; That\u2019s a 10.7% jump.&nbsp; Unless you\u2019re living in Zimbabwe, inflation isn\u2019t nearly that bad.</p><p>But wait, you say!&nbsp; You thought <a href=\"https://www.namecheap.com/blog/icann-allows-com-price-increases-gets-more-money/#:~:text=Price%20Increases%20Verisign%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20increase,annually%20during%202026-2029%2C%20then%20another%20two%20year%20\u201cfreeze\u201d.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ICANN only allowed Verisign to increases by 7% each year</a> for the next 3 years, so how can they get away with 10.7%?!?</p><p>That\u2019s because <a href=\"https://onlinedomain.com/2021/02/12/domain-name-news/verisign-will-increase-the-com-price-from-7-85-to-8-39/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">that\u2019s wholesale</a>.&nbsp; NameSilo (and others) are increasing their fees by in excess of what Verisign is charging them.</p><p><strong>So watcha gonna do?&nbsp; Stick with NameSilo because it\u2019s a hassle to move, or find another registrar that isn\u2019t increasing as much, or\u2026?&nbsp; Let us know in the comments below!</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div class=\"relpost-thumb-wrapper\"><div class=\"relpost-thumb-container\"><h3>Related posts:</h3><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-container\"><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/eu-domains-only-e12-for-10-years-may-3rd-to-12th/\"><div class=\"relpost-custom-block-single\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\".eu Domains: Only \u20ac12 for 10 years, May 3rd to 12th!\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/eu-domain-150x150.png) no-repeat scroll 0% 0%; width: 150px; height: 150px;\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-single-text\" style=\"font-family: Arial;  font-size: 12px;  color: #333333;\">.eu Domains: Only \u20ac12 for 10 years, May 3rd to 12th!</div></div></a><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/a-little-note-on-lowendbox-domain/\"><div class=\"relpost-custom-block-single\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"A Little Note on LowEndBox Domain (and Chance to Win 4VPS.com!)\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://low